OL,3,CLib Dem MP denied entry to Hong Kong
OL,4,Cto visit her son
OL,6,FA Lib Dem MP has been denied entry to
OL,7,FHong Kong to visit her son and
OL,8,Fgrandchild by Chinese authorities, a
OL,9,Fmove the foreign secretary has
OL,10,Fdescribed as "deeply concerning."
OL,12,FWera Hobhouse was denied entry to Hong
OL,13,FKong on Thursday after she had
OL,14,Ftravelled to the territory to visit
OL,15,Fher son, who has lived there since
OL,16,F2019, and new grandson.
OL,18,FShe is believed to be the first MP to
OL,19,Fbe refused entry to the former British
OL,20,Fcolony since it was handed back to
OL,21,FChina in 1997.
