OL,3,CLib Dem MP denied entry to Hong Kong
OL,4,Cto visit her son
OL,6,FMs Hobhouse, a member of the Inter-
OL,7,FParliamentary Alliance on China (Ipac)
OL,8,Fwhich criticises Beijing's handling of
OL,9,Fhuman rights, told The Times she had
OL,10,Fbeen given no explanation for being
OL,11,Frefused entry to Hong Kong.
OL,13,FDescribing the decision as "cruel",
OL,14,Fshe added: "My son was waiting at the
OL,15,Fother end at arrivals. I couldn't even
OL,16,Fsee him and give him a hug and I
OL,17,Fhadn't seen him in a year."
