OL,3,CLib Dem MP denied entry to Hong Kong
OL,4,Cto visit her son
OL,6,FHer parliamentary colleagues expressed
OL,7,Foutrage at the decision, with Lib Dem
OL,8,Fleader Sir Ed Davey saying it was
OL,9,F"heartless" and "totally unacceptable".
OL,11,FParty foreign affairs spokesman Calum
OL,12,FMiller said the decision was "truly
OL,13,Fshocking behaviour by the Hong Kong
OL,14,Fauthorities" and called on Foreign
OL,15,FSecretary David Lammy to meet Ms
OL,16,FHobhouse "and then call the Chinese
OL,17,Fambassador for an explanation".
