OL,6,FMs Hobhouse herself also called on Mr
OL,7,FLammy to raise the issue with China,
OL,8,Fdescribing the decision as a "cruel
OL,9,Fand upsetting blow" and "an insult to
OL,10,Fall parliamentarians".
OL,12,FMr Lammy said: "It is deeply
OL,13,Fconcerning to hear that an MP on a
OL,14,Fpersonal trip has been refused entry
OL,15,Fto Hong Kong.
